                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A great diadem urchin\u2019s spines can swivel to face any approaching creature. Any creature that attacks a great diadem urchin with an unarmed strike or a natural attack, or any Large or smaller creature that attacks with a onehanded weapon or light weapon, is automatically attacked by the hunter urchin\u2019s spines as an immediate action. If the spines hit, they can poison the target as well."
